{"id":209760,"type":1,"name":"ルシフェルの右手","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ae/75/209760_J2ApB.jpg","summary":"　　在非洲某国投身医疗志工活动的外科医生·胜海由宇，被捲入当地内战中，看到眼前不断上演的杀戮，为了保卫自己，拿起步枪，射杀了来袭的士兵。归国之后，他流浪到了横滨。在右臂上留下「失格医生」的烙印的胜海，在机缘巧合下遇见了另一位医生，将他重新导正，回到行医之路。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>圣堂叛医 路西法的右手</li><li><span>册数: </span>6</li><li><span>话数: </span>66</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/8776\">芹沢直樹</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/128\">講談社</a>、<a href=\"/person/7611\">尖端出版</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8155\">モーニング</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Lucifer's Right Hand</li><li><span>开始: </span>2010-02-25(2010年13号)</li><li><span>结束: </span>2011-09-29(2011年44号)</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1,"doing":1},"staff":[{"id":8776,"image":"","name":"芹沢直樹","desc":"作者"},{"id":7611,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6d/b5/7611_prsn_9285i.jpg","name":"台湾尖端","desc":"出版社"},{"id":128,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2f/b1/128_prsn_nHh14.jpg","name":"讲谈社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8155,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/16/8f/8155_prsn_oNMmI.jpg","name":"Morning","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":209754,"name":"ルシフェルの右手 (01)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/a7/a5/209754_jp.jpg"},{"id":209755,"name":"ルシフェルの右手 (02)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/08/0b/209755_jp.jpg"},{"id":209756,"name":"ルシフェルの右手 (03)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/35/d4/209756_jp.jpg"},{"id":209757,"name":"ルシフェルの右手 (04)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/ee/10/209757_jp.jpg"},{"id":209758,"name":"ルシフェルの右手 (05)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/f1/75/209758_jp.jpg"},{"id":209759,"name":"ルシフェルの右手 (06)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/e0/5b/209759_jp.jpg"}]}